{"tid":988581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[準備又贏] 加拿大司法部：美國須在1月30日前提出引渡孟晚舟","createTime":"2019-01-20T07:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T04:10:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"58af30551562b7a555cb1425dc5547a29fcf3d75","tid":988581,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"加拿大司法部：美國須在1月30日前提出引渡孟晚舟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190120/bkn-20190120150435603-0120_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190120%2Fbkn-20190120150435603-0120_00972_001.html&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b7d17e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190120/bkn-20190120150435603-0120_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國科技巨頭華為太子女孟晚舟被加拿大當局扣留一案，本月底將進入關鍵時期。加拿大司法部發言人麥克努德（Ian McLeod）回覆當地媒體查詢時指出，美國最遲須在1月30日前向加方要求引渡孟晚舟，但目前美方尚未提出要求。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麥克努德亦在回覆電郵中指，美國提出引渡要求時，必須同時提交相關證明文件，如果收到美方要求，加拿大政府再有30日時間，以決定是否繼續處理案件。 <br />\n</span><br />\n有熟識引渡法律的加拿大律師則指，如果美國逾期仍未提出引渡要求，等同「為加拿大打開了釋放孟晚舟的大門」，更指司法部長屆時有義務放人。"},{"pid":"397f21c580d65619ebc24bfe6de3e6f8b37ff3d5","tid":988581,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"要圍牆定要晚晚舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3558017aa38741ff11295036345fc6f8abd1dc06","tid":988581,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:03:35.000Z","msg":"慢慢周<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15575ab953db9fbf331efe0f66ffb705c38eca7d","tid":988581,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6564a08f9ffafdba83f85b7d6022ee5fefd5fed9","tid":988581,"uid":116572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite